Hello there fellow hardcore fisherman's outthere!  I guess i will start by introducing my self  lol I'm Andre and I live in the "big" town of sturgeon falls , Ontario ! I love to fish and enjoy every second on the water, rain or shine i love to fish for anything that swims! If it swims I fish it ! If anybody out there needs some info about the northbay, temagami , or marten river area lakes and rivers give me a shout ! I'd be glad to help you if I can or if you are coming up in this area and want a fishing partner I'd be glad too I may be young (25) but i've been fishing since i can hold a rod  a snoopy rod for the matter of fact lol i have over 20 years experience in fishing and fished for all kinds of species of fish! Glad to be on OFC ! Hope to see you on the water !!!  BORN TO FISH! FORCED TO WORK!
Welcome aboard Andre! Congrats to you, you're the very first member to post his introduction in italics. I shouldn't be surprised though. Everyone in Sturgeon is a little slanted.
